Package fr.u_paris.gla.project.graph

package fr.u_paris.gla.project.graph
Graph package provides the model for our application, the representation of the network as java objects.

  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Graph
    Java object representation of the transport Network, holds the lines, sublines, stops etc...
    Line
    A class to describe a line in the Network
    Stop
    Représente un arrêt dans un réseau de transport, avec sa position géographique, les horaires de passage pour chaque sous-ligne qui y passe, et les connexions avec les arrêts adjacents.
    Subline
    A class to describe a subline in the Network.
    TwoDTree
    A 2DTree implementation for a faster spatial search ( for connectStopsByWalking ) Class was written in the last week of development hence why it's only used for connecting stops by walking, which isn't even an useful functionnality since itinerary searches are same or worse and the algorithm takes exponentially more time to find a result.
